#
# how to install docker on Win8
#
	# binary:
		# docker-toolbox  	https://www.docker.com/products/docker-toolbox
		# boot2docker is deprecated https://github.com/boot2docker/windows-installer/releases/tag/v1.8.0	
		# document:		http://www.kancloud.cn/thinkphp/docker-guide/39725
	# usage:
	
	#	document:		https://docs.docker.com/engine/getstarted/
	#	For more examples and ideas, visit:
						https://docs.docker.com/userguide/


	create a shortcut of bash.exe (in %GIT_HOME%)
	kick off "Docker QuickStart Terminal" ("C:\Program Files\Git\bin\bash.exe" --login -i "C:\Program Files\Docker Toolbox\start.sh")
	<=
		docker is configured to use the default machine with IP 192.168.99.100
		For help getting started, check out the docs at https://docs.docker.com
		
		Start interactive shell
		Welcome to Git (version 1.9.5-preview20141217)

$ docker version
